# Code of Conduct

All participants in this project are expected to abide by the [Contributor Covenant](https://www.contributor-covenant.org/).

## Our Pledge

We as members, contributors, and leaders pledge to make participation in our community a harassment-free experience for everyone.

## Our Standards

- Be respectful and considerate
- Use welcoming and inclusive language
- Be respectful of differing viewpoints and experiences
- Accept constructive criticism graciously

## Our Responsibilities

- Foster a welcoming and respectful environment
- Report unacceptable behavior
- Support open communication

## Enforcement

Instances of abusive, harassing, or otherwise unacceptable behavior may be reported to the project maintainers.
